  "title": "JUNIOR EVENTS EXECUTIVE (Training provided)",
  "description": "<p>🌟 <strong>Join Our Events Customer Service Team!</strong> 🚀</p><p>We’re a fast-growing, people-focused company passionate about helping young individuals <strong>develop skills, gain confidence, and grow their careers</strong>. If you’re energetic, creative, and love working with people, this could be your moment to shine! ✨</p><p><br /><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p>🎯 Assist in planning and running events, roadshows, and promotional campaigns<br />💬 Represent well-known brands and engage directly with customers<br />📚 Learn valuable skills in communication, branding, and sales<br />🤝 Build strong relationships with clients, partners, and teammates</p><p><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>✨ Outgoing, positive, and eager to learn<br />🗣 Confident communicator and strong team player<br />🎓 No experience required — <strong>full training provided</strong></p><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><p>🚀 Clear career progression and leadership development<br />💸 Performance incentives, bonuses, and travel opportunities 🌏<br />🎓 Hands-on experience in marketing and customer engagement<br />🤝 A fun, inclusive, and energetic team culture</p><p>📩 <strong>Ready to create memorable experiences and grow your career? Apply now!</strong> 🎯</p>",
